//img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/235946_3a065c14cc2bcbd4eb03bcdd77991318.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F235946_3a065c14cc2bcbd4eb03bcdd77991318.png&h=7be82773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/192852_c55bfca827914b85e2237a7b04a13847.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F192852_c55bfca827914b85e2237a7b04a13847.png&h=8b68fed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoYXFQ6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoYXFQ6.png&h=216310d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jj0MOfG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjj0MOfG.png&h=28005817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n改名都無撚用<br />\n<br />\n麻煩其他人copy 番俾樓主睇，佢block 左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826db94a48c65b4261f356842134db27fcc61731","tid":1015504,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:24:08.000Z","msg":"我都想去英國留學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾個長期病搞到困死香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba46871f07264d2036632a1893db610e5b224f6","tid":1015504,"uid":69531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"我做水記 暫時未見過有同事ou grad"},{"pid":"81f706643c981538d0158bedf4ab5dbe0980150f","tid":1015504,"uid":235477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"鯨大都有醒水識做人嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46209358fe04008a2990d30129f684b752c823e","tid":1015504,"uid":177724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"邊個同你講big4要神人先入到"},{"pid":"e9e4b6d9a641a148c85fea0703c74468517d2df9","tid":1015504,"uid":92439,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"每年得幾個fresh grad入到<br />\n仲要靠RP 同做intern先有機<br />\n利申 今年grad"},{"pid":"3edeeec348a8e4aaa2a21728ca7fb50fe5aca0d5","tid":1015504,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"考牌冇分咩學校<br />\n考到就得<br />\n大把外國u都做到啦"},{"pid":"4c300654638f0e04b6b600cc9a8f4971b47f5dfd","tid":1015504,"uid":137217,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"觀念錯誤<br />\n做Big4唔係代表勁,big4人工亦唔係高commercial好多<br />\n除非你唔係做fi<br />\n做fi好多都高過big4<br />\nbig4係升得快<br />\n但都係用命換返嚟下下做到12點<br />\n重點係你有冇牌<br />\n冇牌做big4一樣係舊垃圾<br />\nbig4 其實長期缺人,肯做就入到<br />\n除非你無牌<br />\n講難入係因為你fresh grad+無牌姐<br />\n本身做開呢行有牌既人想入100%入到啦<br />\n除非你做到partner啦,咁就勁喇"},{"pid":"c531892406689ec99a1ffd3eec01422f1eb95b44","tid":1015504,"uid":104924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba46871f07264d2036632a1893db610e5b224f6","tid":1015504,"uid":69531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T05:29:56.000Z","msg":"我做水記 暫時未見過有同事ou grad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"點會冇"},{"pid":"2bc622842c00f1b85e5414cec5569619cbadaed9","tid":1015504,"uid":171594,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"Big 4主要係收三大中等至中上<br />\nPoly/city 最top個班<br />\n間中有幾個bu/lingu<br />\nOu真係未見過"},{"pid":"d8da97b2c0f635155f55d184d2caf847e37ccd49","tid":1015504,"uid":153811,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"我舊時間bank有位ou programmer見識同諗野方底比3大仲高，又肯做，結果10知月升左，其他人就年半。<br />\n<br />\n咁當然100個ou都冇出到佢一個啦，我唔知啦，佢係個間bank歷來第一位ou perm 員工。<br />\n<br />\nBig4唔知係咪請入過tier 2 或以上的bank啦，不過睇成績出身的想法係好on9,有錢人課哂金點差極d仔女都唔差過普通人啦。"},{"pid":"61fa9ccdeea8aa8f47b233a564560f9a8e1e6b2d","tid":1015504,"uid":125258,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(Acc) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Accounting, 將來就可以用會計監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫上司公司和稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"9d706575ef3d7f51201516d309eb2cffd66c2f6f","tid":1015504,"uid":103061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"見過有人 ou local 轉 second tier 再轉入 big4"}]}